      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As a woman and mother, I was very much offended by your report on the model who served as a table for sushi (''Selling the Sizzle Even Though It's Sushi,'' April 18).</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As a woman and mother, I was very much offended by your report on the model who served as a table for sushi (''Selling the Sizzle Even Though It's Sushi,'' April 18).</p>
        <p>Your article suggested that getting paid $1,100 made this somehow less objectionable. Since when is prostitution condoned by your paper?</p>
        <p>JOAN KNOEBEL  Madison, Wis.</p>
      </block>
